{"type":null,"faqId":46041,"title":"拍摄的照片没有地理位置信息","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、检查GPS开关是否打开，“设置--位置服务”，定位模式选择：准确度高、耗电量低，使用网络定位，不能选择“仅限设备”；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、在相机应用的设置中，开启地理位置功能，在图库应用的设置中，打开显示拍摄地点；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、需要在使用数据流量或者WLAN环境下，才能显示地理位置；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、拍照地点尽量选择室外空旷地方；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5、某些产品不支持照片右下角显示所在城市，请点击照片的详细信息，检查是否有经纬度信息；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>6、拍照的时候，通知栏会显示“正在搜索GPS”，连续多拍几张照片，等在通知栏显示“已确定GPS位置”。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1821","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375610000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":19,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"照片,,地理位置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}